We are happy to present the first episode of Interkerbal

Max Kerman, a failed kerbonaut, hopes to demonstrate that Kerbin is flat thanks to the rocket he designed himself. Between humor, conspiracy and space, this first episode will introduce you to the world of Interkerbal, but also that of guests appreciated by the team such as Defakator (Kefakator) and Stardust (Starkust).

English and Spanish subtitles ; we are looking for translators and voice dubbing !!!

 

Edited June 19, 2020 by Kapu
Thanks, we search voice actors for english, spain...etc
